{"title":"Poet and Audience","author":{"name":"Erik Campbell"},"publishDate":"2011-05-02","lines":[{"line":"I","stanza":1,"number":1},{"line":"The Argument: You Wondered Why You Weren’t Published","stanza":1,"number":2},{"line":"It’s because the postman has opened","stanza":2,"number":3},{"line":"All your submissions and kept them","stanza":2,"number":4},{"line":"Tucked your words, as it were, under","stanza":2,"number":5},{"line":"His proverbial, federal wing.","stanza":2,"number":6},{"line":"And just so you know,","stanza":3,"number":7},{"line":"Your love poems work.","stanza":3,"number":8},{"line":"He reads them to his wife in bed","stanza":3,"number":9},{"line":"Before what has recently become","stanza":3,"number":10},{"line":"Most lyrical sex; he even adds","stanza":4,"number":11},{"line":"A few verbs here and there","stanza":4,"number":12},{"line":"For the sake of flow.","stanza":4,"number":13},{"line":"II","stanza":5,"number":14},{"line":"The Consolation","stanza":5,"number":15},{"line":"But you’ll be pleased to know","stanza":6,"number":16},{"line":"He generally leaves your","stanza":6,"number":17},{"line":"Enjambment alone","stanza":6,"number":18},{"line":"And understands the way irony","stanza":6,"number":19},{"line":"Goes; a fulcrum for your failure","stanza":7,"number":20},{"line":"And his formally elegiac evenings","stanza":7,"number":21},{"line":"Which he now has the diction","stanza":7,"number":22},{"line":"And courage to call epiphanic.","stanza":7,"number":23},{"line":"His only regret","stanza":8,"number":24},{"line":"Is that you aren’t","stanza":8,"number":25},{"line":"More prolific.","stanza":8,"number":26}]}